cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

Reasoning: The paper deals with semantic instance segmentation, which is a computer vision task, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new algorithm for joint graph partitioning and labeling, which involves optimization, making cs.LG and cs.AI likely sub-categories as well. The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which falls under cs.CL. Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed algorithm on both 2D urban scenes and 3D microscopy volume, indicating that it could also fall under cs.MM.
